留电动汽车的税收抵免。同时，特朗普和共和党参议员讨论了如何减少该法案&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/nofCt2gQfar_5rnqq5_iTfH_0DsHdMnO11b3BjHslxBbGlGqs9rg10yJgr7C4LJ9BpifvFXL7IZ8r4e4gLbfn-RxlgFABkzjzroNaBkcCJFZrqxsC4N780y-ebMkg9ky2_1BJxxsv9bCqzwgv_B00Qxw_G9MMt2ucyy3qXt3f3zQlqKHUL5W7Za4RgyHQH1Ai0_9Xw2ddCPdshKbG1MoRuFsgHqPN0Vi2vYfudaQWw_D0JL5OWpdjQ5sEY1p33GbQuewhr-KTyMkX64_8Jq54UMmfA/nnHNd5WVJ-KfkrrpdAsftBiLI87H0Whj/9" target="_blank"&gt;众议院版本&lt;/a&gt;中40,000美元的盐分扣除的方法。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普与世界强者进行谈判的“交易艺术”&lt;/strong&gt;方法并不完全&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/bWt_rGSYDWY7FcUY3I9W7x6Q-U2qhp1CgsutN7SR_Ax9LmRQCys-6U54ojNW3SNOO0odEDsENBPxb6-fwvVNgLodK7Q7A6jz_zGmK9xX6ERIwNC8xsvKmd0aNOM6R9K7emyIeHd8CTlgI1pHTOi0u2JlXNGJbAoPXUSJpbCvrIC3Q1qiugGq7b_C3GDtJ8BHgXKMDc5X8hD0MTLOZj8sraaTuhDQpPb0fa5hkJAcR0OFHveg-vziP25ZoNqjSBHCAJblWIMhHiXcVO-PwYgSI4QyvA/Vlhs1eO9hOiCuo8gUaNfdTZVZD9D4I1A/9" target="_blank"&gt;计划&lt;/a&gt;。在过去的48小时内，他被俄罗斯，中国和伊朗的领导人拒绝。业务高管正在失去对经济前景的信心，这是美国总统连任后的浮力情绪的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/MEr65OMLNv8hiuVWfC4fBH7RzhJr3yH1SHT4bOXoBgM7cSo45_3yol7QREnO-rEgsEoePQY_a8rka7s2L1k7mpXqTP80nHYpNnJsRBdKUNqUeBPSUY-F9yAhNO4hIk9Gwb7GDuSL-9ku_PysqkxfyrDe-vjvV4O4TkuYiE4Rx0dJzDsJKXfsC0M8ADRSnmvkSoxpQhZ55B-Ed6UA5d07DzB4TXs1U8kwjlBj7fAdhOxBAlOSE0raiys_Napkx9U2fTtXFHon_LHOJECx4DiLQvO3cA/uhmpAH3mPZzQExsAnYYwUh6in7BsJqLb/9" target="_blank"&gt;急剧逆转&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/eyngQQ4N2EpaZplCYMvYBUKJe-NMeG55hR2_0j87xKKN2m5WWaW4hjBQvcS8eAsEbxR1samEimpTRrRazwuhCWb0s77ePhw30PvGGQ9gnv2_ozWOfyZRLlH4lwCy15MDnX9W55Ddp-kIaY-5EyeB2DyDGcPPPeMEySiF79y46DYw3UvlSF4WTOhp49QyX7hO8LyKpS4nJaqieCSAkWI08thGqBCfYcZ97vXb7an3ltDTduX4z92IIyKsnJxb70_TFHOCSeKoeox79gXibha20jwHmA/P6fhPAI7LkydaCdnfxoJDWHOFLVYheoa/9" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&