k0jsvmMYa-rNMHihmkW3_kG_BJHNUVg/VCxq4cRMliFxZKYC5jRVE1UjX-ztXHg4/9" target="_blank"&gt;可能会出错。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普禁止&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/9hxE6mXkOCXYeNPeD41V8CaX2v8GfzlRdGv4oYKcwHZuYxQZayOFLdNR-A5rNAO1tLM_x7U66noK9SzFr4f6ec9lZCIgsqxO3s2sOcIZXC5J6fFUq9FXjYJdsrKgxLwaTrU0qaKTt1urUtcXlJKn740dPPv2fODtCcDtZ9w_4aYiWyJqcCy8iZUxumZzVlPWW9NBTAc4laP3WM_UGoOzxCvFSUEI-2e0BnPDr0x5LYA6wGVYEPeWTRC5ZoHq5_U6tJQgiqjxgldjxn8u_OY1HWM8vQ/oaSf83PlR5a5-qtrCX2aXv2ii3qe6OaX/9" target="_blank"&gt;来自12个国家进入美国的个人&lt;/a&gt;，从他的第一任期起恢复了最有争议的措施之一。这&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/LCXNYGaXzwBEhsCLUhayxV4wSAQKJJErOlVFuGBJt8_SKSp-_0nzyCjLPgo_-J0idsdNvFAksr5D1JFTquNburQdfnhcveZAl1VHfJC95YQg8AYX3csH7bPfjVDPwg__YX-dc-yK4O7vnpH2wwS5F7IU1Ivv8_vlB3AS4Xj1O1qpx7YWsxEpZWUn-QkR2YeXzrzpRF0PZzti1i_7awt8mrfzCk3zdzsRT1alJcqaI3pKPebMY_zJsYNyFa1eplXhEdnC4eUrh3q5SotxXJI5IRs8Ag/HbpcpTILyKV90Zicr5ueiVcKMALJQGev/9" target="_blank"&gt;也部分限制了包括古巴和老挝在内的七个国家的人们的进入&lt;/a&gt;。他还签署了一项行政诉讼，该行动阻止外国国民进入美国在哈佛学习。这可能使他的政府&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/GXWv9vxMOxHderoB7vcLeCBECuRc8BLNTJeKfm6vo06we1PvveBl2gb4tpjRaQfmFhzaeDXvMC10YDmlDt-xUlkqKB6z7Trl-39gUTwHCGeIRCQZZ_y-jL0vzCVjujjD5i-zg11x-yl-3KgB837w0olZYYb2K3Hxj4rXMD2kADKj2k4ewlQYvkuZVUaqZfWPkd_0s7ohcgaH3Bx_q63UG9_vmdzv_h7__0-p6vvWKtTbr4869V9q1hXe7i9fFLZ6fEpPdD2bWN41Lg6xB3dsN7uQiA/_g4eVm1VLE6lwwNsGD0CMWO2iSHwKV_i/9" target="_blank"&gt;避开了一项裁决&lt;/a&gt;，使大学得以暂时继续入学。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/mkB_Wlk_-ihXgnoEZq19JheAazJ5-mNss8Ni6SS-3jykhFfTXCRssUtXEuV9OJOpTCJMRB3MVX2W5X6yCUFZvEbQ_Ju0o8ga69zyR8z51Vn97m6_c0-CfmHrnfR-WHD5byiI1winP_mEe6yEDlk-1-PbfZcaMDxy2t5j8SINl1Wa7oE4JyQQ3YGIJWrb8LVuFhMfKywRG47N1KI0sZZPjIV3rktKLMgRK9Uw3E7QRjckPmGte5TuqMDUh-iY-VcBWCtNXEwfNNYbxybXq9ktz3Lv-A/5LXJpBSrQS4UzXJLmgA6iyMWjoZdnNf5/9" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioch5m_hmZ10/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="alt" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioch5m_hmZ10/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" width="530" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;在市场上，&lt;/strong&gt;随着贸易商从日本的提升，国债&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/tQcpQ7M4OWBge0oP1dGYqakCjwr_rd3CO7DdINf8MLsAy6AvsyUqBx8gQfD53-igh8YMwn2HKjOmbP8MzLagXB9Nf2mmiBAwYMmNibFIX0l6gmdRX6eccrZ-mNRIBeN9wueKERg87oXnrHJV6fodD3encynh0-9fQzdI7HPRN4zjy_S9J9lQeogH3dWOVQ50A1qXyhT3Odx44lZ_rhXaVEAWuw2wiatJfVldJe5uydohA8nQuIkq0l74qM70w1ON0uBKQguZ-u9XIAkgQ5vOk5c9EQ/GS_vy3l-BYR_cHbxr9qFuMesNrfQkBAs/9" target="_blank"&gt;更高&lt;/a&gt;，那里的政府债券拍卖比所担心的要好。欧洲中央银行看上去几乎可以肯定会再次&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/47IB4SVFHhQ9m-f4KXQuvcB-aL7mdeQDfU4F59ziyyx2Ih-hMXnj70S6kecYgKdam0osNnmSFbtGOrM9PtHfsYFjvtegyb42S8EA5tYz3T27HEp_8lf0_mMgfjE0u2sZIuR7io81M5AyIb3UU2JRcKcFJrQDkno9BWESmpTrI5y6v318GQt2trDJzUFOJJLUkSEinNl8qRKB6XR2yM_qLYkheK5HXBkS1IVB0IAthDvLBZFfeIA6WsX0G6fPIs6rEx7OGW8Rouo9R4AFUAnSh9DS8w/4gR4Drwrdus5AZcaa6lDQu3bCvwvQUZl/9" target="_blank"&gt;降低利率&lt;/a&gt;，但是不断改变美国贸易威胁将使决策者试图制定新的经济预测。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="2" style="padding: 0 0px;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message